About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger," starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2", the sixth film in the YRF Spy Universe, starring Hrithik Roshan, NTR and Kiara Advani, directed by Ayan Mukerji, released on 14 August 2025. "Alpha", the seventh film in the franchise and Hindi cinema‚Äôs first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, will release on 25 December 2025.

snippet.title: #Video | Najariya Najar Se |Godfather | #Khesari Lal Yadav |#Priyanka Singh |New Bhojpuri Song 2025
snippet.description:
"Najariya Najar Se" is the latest romantic Bhojpuri song of 2025, released under Times Music Bhojpuri from the upcoming movie "Godfather." Sung by the dynamic duo Khesari Lal Yadav and Priyanka Singh, this love track beautifully captures the essence of romance through heartfelt lyrics and soulful melodies. With its catchy composition and visually stunning official video, the song is quickly becoming a fan favorite across social media and music platforms.

The music video showcases a compelling love story blending traditional Bhojpuri vibes with a modern cinematic touch. Whether you're a fan of Bhojpuri cinema, love songs, or the chart-topping voice of Khesari Lal Yadav, "Najariya Najar Se" is a must-watch and a must-listen.

#newbhojpurisong #romanticbhojpurisong #bhojpurigana #bhojpurisong #bhojpurilovesong  #khesarilalyadav #priyankasingh

About SHINE HUNT :
* On our channel we create –∞ trailer teaser *
Also known as recut trailers, involve collecting multiple pieces of film footage from one or multiple movies A New And Fresh Story, editing them to create a new trailer. Trailer teaser Glimpse are often created for a movie that does not exist now or to change the genre of an existing film..
The trailer mashups are not only a user generated form of digital creativity but a way to create anticipation for future releases, working in tandem with current movie trailers. Movie trailers are designed to give minimal plot detail and to create hype and anticipation. Fan made trailer mashups allow the audience to perform their own cinematic spin on current movie footage. This allows the trailer to focus on a specific actor or portion of the film. It could even change the plot or genre of the film entirely .                                      .----SHINE HUNT CHANNEL----

snippet.title: Rippan Swaamy Official Trailer | Vijay Raghavendra | Ashwini Chandrashekar | Kishor Mudubidire | PRK
snippet.description:
Panchaanana Films productions in association with PRK Audio
presents
Rippan Swaamy - A rural thriller set in the fictional Malnad village of Snana Kopa.
The story unfolds after the mysterious suicide of Rippan Swaamy, leading to a trail of secrets, drama, and suspense. As the mystery deepens, the truth behind his name and death slowly unravels.

The film is set to release in theatres on August 29.
 üéµ Listen to the soulful songs exclusively on PRK Audio.

Production House: Panchaanana Films
Directed by: Kishor Mudubidire
Produced by: Panchaanana Films

Cast: Vijay Raghavendra, Ashwini Chandrashekar, Prakash Thuminadu, Vajradheer Jain, Yamuna Srinidhi, Krishnamurthy Kavattaru, Santhosh Shetty

DOP: Ranghanath C M
Editor: Shashank Narayana
Music and Background Score: Samuel ABY
Audio Label: PRK Audio
Trailer Cut: Shashank Narayana
Trailer Voice Over: Nayana Nagaraj

Co-Producers: Ashwitha Parikshith, Manjunath Thuppur, Akshay Kumar, Neeraj Shetty, Prajwal Shetty, Preeta Ramanagoudar, Reshma D.S, Sathish Bangera, Varuna, Raghavendra Baliga, Sushmitha Rahul, Pradeep Krishnamurthy, Naveen Kumar Maroor, Yogesh G M, Padmanabh, Naveen Kumar Ullal, Ramprasad Mudubidire, Meghana B P, Ankith Kishor

About T-Series Fox 

On our channel we create –∞ trailer mashups ‚ñ∑
Also known as recut trailers, involve collecting multiple pieces of film footage from one or multiple movies and Add Our Own Dialogues To Make A New And Fresh Story, editing them to create a new trailer. Trailer mashups are often created for a movie that does not exist now or to change the genre of an existing film. These are derivative works as defined by the United States Copyright Act 17 U.S.C. ¬ß 101, and as such, may find protection from copyright claims under the doctrine of fair use.

The trailer mashups are not only a user generated form of digital creativity but a way to create anticipation for future releases, working in tandem with current movie trailers. Movie trailers are designed to give minimal plot detail and to create hype and anticipation. Fan made trailer mashups allow the audience to perform their own cinematic spin on current movie footage. This allows the trailer to focus on a specific actor or portion of the film. It could even change the plot ocr genre of the film entirely.

This video is a parody DUE to its derivative/ transformative nature this video is covered as a Fair Use of material.

Welcome to our Tamil Devotional Channel, your ultimate destination for soulful and uplifting Tamil devotional songs. Dive into the divine with our carefully curated collections designed to inspire and bring peace to your soul every day of the week.

Daily Devotional Songs:
* Monday Tamil Devotional Songs
* Tuesday Tamil Devotional Songs
* Wednesday Tamil Devotional Songs
* Thursday Tamil Devotional Songs
* Friday Tamil Devotional Songs
* Saturday Tamil Devotional Songs
* Sunday Tamil Devotional Songs

Special Devotional Collections:
* Shiva Tamil Devotional Songs: Celebrate the power and grace of Lord Shiva.
* Vishnu Tamil Devotional Songs: Immerse in the blessings of Lord Vishnu.
* Muruga Tamil Devotional Songs: Invoke the valor and blessings of Lord Muruga.
* Hanuman Tamil Devotional Songs: Feel the strength and devotion of Lord Hanuman.
* Amman Tamil Devotional Songs: Honor the divine mother in her various forms.
* Saibaba Tamil Devotional Songs: Seek the blessings of Shirdi Sai Baba.
* Balaji Tamil Devotional Songs: Worship Lord Venkateswara with these soulful songs.
* Lakshmi Tamil Devotional Songs: Attract prosperity with hymns for Goddess Lakshmi.
* Devi Tamil Devotional Songs: Praise the supreme goddess Devi in her many avatars.
* Ganesh Tamil Devotional Songs: Start your day with prayers to Lord Ganesha.

Special Occasions and Deities:
* Amavasai Tamil Devotional Songs: Songs for the new moon day rituals.
* Pradosham Tamil Devotional Songs: Hymns for the auspicious Pradosham period.
* Ashta Lakshmi Tamil Devotional Songs: Songs dedicated to the eight forms of Goddess Lakshmi.
* Vinayagar Tamil Devotional Songs: Devotions for the remover of obstacles, Lord Vinayagar.
* Ganapathi Tamil Devotional Songs: Invoke blessings from Lord Ganapathi.
* Surya Tamil Devotional Songs: Worship the Sun God, Surya, with these melodies.
* Sani Tamil Devotional Songs: Appease Lord Sani with these devotional tracks.
* Guru Tamil Devotional Songs: Songs to honor Guru and seek his wisdom.
* Perumal Tamil Devotional Songs: Devote to Lord Perumal with these spiritual songs.
* Navagraha Tamil Devotional Songs: Balance your energies with songs for the nine planets.

Subscribe now and join our spiritual journey. Like, share, and hit the bell icon to stay updated with our latest devotional uploads. May these divine songs bring peace, prosperity, and positivity to your life.
